Baseline Version 2 - Mobile-optimized WMM2026 application

Key improvements in V2:
- Mobile-optimized standings table with 2x2 Final Four grid
- iPhone-compatible column widths (46px space saved)
- Compact table rows and reduced padding
- Smart word breaking for player names (12 character limit)
- Fixed logo URL generation for production deployment
- Optimized horizontal layout for mobile devices
- Enhanced speed and performance
- All team logos working with ESPN URLs

This version represents the mobile-optimized baseline with significant
UI improvements for better mobile user experience.

