    Fix logo URL generation for production deployment
    
    - Force ESPN URLs in production instead of local paths
    - Local logo cache was returning /logos/ paths that don't exist on Vercel
    - Now falls back to ESPN URLs in production environment
    - Fixes 400 errors for team logos

